Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: MITRE data fetch fails

Solution: Check internet connectivity; verify GitHub URL is accessible; add timeout parameter to requests
Issue: Matplotlib display error

Solution: Set backend before importing pyplot: matplotlib.use('Agg')
Issue: Draw.io file won't import

Solution: Validate XML structure; ensure proper encoding (UTF-8); check for special characters in labels
Issue: Empty threat list generated

Solution: Verify MITRE CSV was created successfully; check asset type keywords match technique descriptions; ensure pandas DataFrame is not empty
Issue: Python module not found

Solution: Reinstall requirements: pip3 install --upgrade -r requirements.txt
